import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' const Sec05 = ({value}) => { const {wedding, groom, bride} = value; // 카운트다운 변수 const [countdown, setCountdown] = useState({ day: 0, hour: 0, min: 0, sec: 0 }); const targetDate = new Date(wedding.year, wedding.month-1, wedding.date, wedding.hour, wedding.min, 0, 0); useEffect(() => { const interval = setInterval(() => { const todayDate = new Date(); const diff = targetDate - todayDate; setCountdown({ day: Math.floor(diff / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)), hour: Math.floor((diff / (1000 * 60 * 60)) % 24), min: Math.floor((diff / (1000 * 60)) % 60), sec: Math.floor(diff / 1000 % 60) }); }, 1000); // 컴포넌트 언마운트 시 인터벌 정리 return () => clearInterval(interval); }, []); return (
